    "row": 146,
    "rowsha": "Kckjf5IxqYIlXCyJRdkyIcvUSAugIhCyYXz70/2tiVw=",
    "originContent": "To obfuscate your resources and generate an obfuscated AAB, run the following Gradle command in the project's root",
    "translatedContent": "要混淆您的资源并生成混淆的 AAB，请在项目根目录下运行以下 Gradle 命令。:"
  },
  {
    "row": 147,
