  },
  {
    "row": 152,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "此命令将在项目根目录执行混淆过程，混淆后的 AAB 将生成在  "
  },
  {
    "row": 153,
    "rowsha": "qQUKDK3OwVty9L+CjzacZUcE//JOcRzj1t/1qCBWNGA=",
    "originContent": "This command will execute the obfuscation process from the project root, and the obfuscated AAB will be generated in",
