    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 155,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 配置选项"
  },
  {
    "row": 156,
    "rowsha": "V9KSt2YGHWHKhLFXw8vhKEfBj8HIXJIPsF8Xv1NwUTI=",
    "originContent": "## Configuration Options",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 157,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "ResChiper 扩展提供了各种资源混淆的配置选项，包括启用/禁用混淆、指定映射文件、资源白名单等。"
  },
  {
    "row": 158,
    "rowsha": "R302s4VgdQsxZwH/7XCKlXqERQbFw7TDyPfUw+2n8mc=",
    "originContent": "The ResChiper extension provides various configuration options for resource obfuscation, including enabling/disabling",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 159,
    "rowsha": "uIehel6OVQ4o3X4N7bOb3H7vMlt9nVbhKqybeht7i0g=",
    "originContent": "obfuscation, specifying mapping files, white-listing resources, and more.",
    "translatedContent": "- `enableObfuscation`：启用或禁用资源混淆。<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 160,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "- `obfuscationMode`：设置为 `obfuscationMode = \"dir\"` 仅混淆目录，设置为 `obfuscationMode = \"file\"` 仅混淆文件，设置为 `obfuscationMode = \"default\"` 混淆目录和文件。<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 161,
    "rowsha": "lTXQA/tM58thvkYaQJ29nQKIlZZz6kPZrFLNA2dpWdM=",
    "originContent": "- `enableObfuscation`: Enable or disable resource obfuscation.<br>",
    "translatedContent": "- `enableFilterStrings`：按行输入未使用的文件拆分以支持移除字符串。<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 162,
    "rowsha": "14ZoPmmpiRbQTDlIUBr4KA8JM06H89rrGrH6RyTLlMA=",
    "originContent": "- `obfuscationMode`: to obfuscate only directories set `obfuscationMode = \"dir\"`, to obfuscate only files set",
    "translatedContent": "- `enableFileFiltering`：支持过滤 bundle 包中的文件，目前仅支持过滤 `META-INFO/` 和 `lib/` 路径。<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 163,
    "rowsha": "ryFMCW+/+ohlREMMmaV8go5Tea4xHF4kUoDKMcNa0Sk=",
    "originContent": "  `obfuscationMode = \"file\"` and to obfuscate both directory and files set `obfuscationMode = \"default\"`.<br>",
    "translatedContent": "- `obfuscatedBundleName`：混淆后 AAB 文件的名称。<br>"
  },
